ggc.file.ddf
     Data Descriptive File (ISO 8211) reader

ggc.file.ddf-sdts-dlg
     SDTS/DLG reader

Sample data are not come with ggc, but you can obtain
them from either 
     http://www.cs.arizona.edu/icon/oddsends/dlgvu/palo_alto.zip
or
     http://edc.usgs.gov/geodata/.

References

   A DLG Viewer for UNIX
     http://www.cs.arizona.edu/icon/oddsends/dlgvu/

   SDTS
     Home Page   http://mcmcweb.er.usgs.gov/sdts/
     Document    http://mcmcweb.er.usgs.gov/sdts/standard.html

   Usefull documents,
     http://www.3dartist.com/WP/sdts/sdtsnotes.htm
     http://www.jst.go.jp/SIST/handbook/sist11/index.htm

